Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.00,0:21:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七皇位继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修·Vi·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.86,0:22:04.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修!?  可是 你应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该死了 是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.98,0:22:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了  殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.57,0:22:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了返还一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.54,0:23:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾认为这是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个普通学生却要改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.38,0:23:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在太不现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.98,0:23:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只要稍微一想就能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.73,0:24:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能获得契机的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:06.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估计  我所选择的会是...
